<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB4C8ED0DFE5BBC0F" authority="Spaeth" authorityName="Spaeth" authorityYear="1906" box="[148,453,569,590]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Aspidimorpha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="haefligeri">
<emphasis id="5BD4E550BC20181DB4C8ED0DFEE3BC0F" box="[148,381,569,590]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="80">Aspidimorpha haefligeri</emphasis>
Spaeth
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="691F3942BC20181DB4F5ED57FD61BD59" blockId="1.[148,977,611,792]" pageId="1" pageNumber="80">
<emphasis id="5BD4E550BC20181DB4F5ED57FEF0BC39" bold="true" box="[169,366,611,632]" pageId="1" pageNumber="80">New host record:</emphasis>
<collectingCountry id="11B779D2BC20181DB522ED50FD9DBC38" box="[382,515,612,633]" name="Zimbabwe" pageId="1" pageNumber="80">ZIMBABWE</collectingCountry>
, 
<quantity id="AE5894A7BC20181DB64BED50FDC3BC38" box="[535,605,612,633]" metricMagnitude="4" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" unit="km" value="40.0">40 km</quantity>
N Mhangura, Chipiri estate lake, 168379310S, 308069420E, 
<date id="1D1E1F82BC20181DB5CDED4AFD9DBCD2" box="[401,515,638,659]" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" value="1998-09-19">19-IX-1998</date>
, 
<specimenCount id="7FA6F2CBBC20181DB64EED4AFDE3BCD2" box="[530,637,638,659]" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" type="adult">two adults</specimenCount>
. Beetles were taken on leaves of 
<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB4C8EDADFE35BCEF" authority="Taub." authorityName="Taub." box="[148,427,665,686]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Brachystegia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="boehmii">
<emphasis id="5BD4E550BC20181DB4C8EDADFEF9BCEF" box="[148,359,665,686]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="80">Brachystegia boehmii</emphasis>
Taub.
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB5EBEDADFD8CBCEF" box="[439,530,665,686]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Fabaceae</taxonomicName>
. Jolivet and Hawkeswood (1995) record this Old World genus from four plant families, 
<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB619ED87FD31BC89" box="[581,687,691,712]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Asteraceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Asterales" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Asteraceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB6E0ED87FCC9BC89" box="[700,855,691,712]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Convolvulaceae</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB739ED87FC50BC89" box="[869,974,691,712]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Lamiaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Lamiaceae</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB4E0EDFAFEA6BCA2" box="[188,312,718,739]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Verbenaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Lamiales" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Verbenaceae</taxonomicName>
, and accidentally from seven additional plant families, with no record of their occurrence on 
<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB536EDDCFE5BBCBC" box="[362,453,744,765]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Fabaceae</taxonomicName>
. In South Africa, Heron and Borowiec (1997) recorded five species of 
<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB57BEC37FE30BD59" authorityName="Hope" authorityYear="1840" box="[295,430,771,792]" class="Insecta" family="Chrysomelidae" genus="Aspidimorpha" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="5BD4E550BC20181DB57BEC37FE30BD59" box="[295,430,771,792]" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="80">Aspidimorpha</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
exclusively from 
<taxonomicName id="AEA042C1BC20181DB603EC37FD65BD59" box="[607,763,771,792]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Convolvulaceae" kingdom="Plantae" order="Solanales" pageId="1" pageNumber="80" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="family">Convolvulaceae</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
